des:
Jean Mello is the founder of the company Inspirando Sonhos and author of Crônicas Perdidas, Exalando Esperança (Exhaling Hope), Fim de tarde and Intocado. 

To start, just say "Alexa, start Jean Mello Quotes" or "Alexa, open Jean Mello Quotes" to receive a sentence.

At any time, you can say "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
